column5: ryan bonin is not lazy....    if he only knew...   I appreciate them trying to help out but I think they could have toned down the "Bonin" talk.  It's about the Fish-A-Thon and our cause as a group... not me.
Just get healthy for tomorrow, bud!!!
If you like Ryan we can all write letters to the editors and tell them what kind of guy you truly are.  See you bright and early.  Hittin' the road soon for BPS and then Tillsonburg.
